517
00:36:50,106 --> 00:36:52,454
He's the worst kind. He's a cop.

518
00:36:53,375 --> 00:36:57,061
I don't know his name or anything, but I know he's an undercover detective in Vice.

519
00:36:57,184 --> 00:37:00,307
My boyfriend told me that nobody moves any kind of narcotic

