00:37:08,928 --> 00:37:10,552
I didn't know what else to do.

523
00:37:14,815 --> 00:37:17,044
A tisket, a tasket

524
00:37:17,203 --> 00:37:19,987
A green and yellow basket

525
00:37:20,067 --> 00:37:22,734
I wrote a letter to my love

