530
00:37:42,840 --> 00:37:45,977
Hey... did you say Wolfe?

531
00:37:46,194 --> 00:37:47,689
Hey, wait a sec.

532
00:37:47,887 --> 00:37:50,976
You know what? Let me walk you to the gate. I just have this feeling...

533
00:38:25,418 --> 00:38:27,605
Police officer! Stop or I'll shoot!

534
00:38:41,382 --> 00:38:43,087
- Don't stop!
- What do you mean?!

535
00:38:43,143 --> 00:38:44,178
Just trust me.

536
00:39:05,689 --> 00:39:09,210
An eyewitness to murder and an employee of the District Attorney's office

537
00:39:09,276 --> 00:39:11,458
narrowly escaped death here at the airport...

538
00:39:11,544 --> 00:39:15,492
If I don't see some bodies fully dressed and making their way to the car in the next 30 seconds...

539
00:39:15,580 --> 00:39:17,621
