00:39:28,927 --> 00:39:33,177
at the end of an unoccupied jetway dangling three stories in the air.

545
00:39:33,257 --> 00:39:36,965
- Did anyone remember to shut off the TV?
- Fate and a passing luggage carrier intervened, and...

546
00:39:44,994 --> 00:39:48,107
